                    > to 10.0.1.29 via ge-0/1/1
10.0.0.5/32        *[OSPF/10] 00:00:06, metric 65536
                    > to 10.0.1.29 via ge-0/1/1
10.0.0.6/32        *[OSPF/10] 00:00:06, metric 65537
                    > to 10.0.1.29 via ge-0/1/1
10.0.1.0/30        *[OSPF/10] 00:00:06, metric 65537
                    > to 10.0.1.29 via ge-0/1/1
